@node bugs "Unexplained features"

AVB Buglist.

AVB can't differentiate between HAm and nonHAM animations, and needs a
command line switch to display them properly.

x2 code doesn't work without fracturing the display, and has been removed
from release 1.0b

AVB doesn;t like anims with interlaced screen modes.

@endnode


